The protagonist, Ruth, is very weak. His movements
are slow and he doesn't seem very strong, so male
villagers and female warriors will chase after him
if they see him. If caught, it's instant death, so
please be careful.

In exchange, you can save at any time. Be mindful
to save frequently. However, since there is a
possibility of save-locking yourself, it is
recommended to split your save data finely.

If you feel the game speed is slow, there is a
double-speed mode available, and if you're stuck
in the game, you can try the hint function from
the mode selection.
